oss rivers. It search\u00ad es wide areas for food."},{"version":"ruby","text":"RATICATE\u2019s sturdy fangs grow steadily. To keep them ground down, it gnaws on rocks and logs. It may even chew on the walls of houses."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"RATICATE\u2019s sturdy fangs grow steadily. To keep them ground down, it gnaws on rocks and logs. It may even chew on the walls of houses."},{"version":"emerald","text":"A RATICATE\u2019s sturdy fangs grow steadily. To keep them ground down, it gnaws on rocks and logs. It may even chew on the walls of houses."},{"version":"firered","text":"Its rear feet have three toes each. They are webbed, enabling it to swim across rivers."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It uses its whiskers to maintain its balance. It apparently slows down if they are cut off."},{"version":"diamond","text":"It whittles its constantly growing fangs by gnawing on hard things. It can chew apart cinder walls."},{"version":"pearl","text":"It whittles its constantly growing fangs by gnawing on hard things. It can chew apart cinder walls."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It whittles its constantly growing fangs by gnawing on hard things. It can chew apart cinder walls."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Gnaws on anything with its tough fangs. It can even topple concrete buildings by gnawing on them."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its whiskers help it to maintain balance. Its fangs never stop growing, so it gnaws to pare them down."},{"version":"black","text":"It whittles its constantly growing fangs by gnawing on hard things. It can chew apart cinder walls."},{"version":"white","text":"It whittles its constantly growing fangs by gnawing on hard things. It can chew apart cinder walls."},{"version":"black-2","text":"With its long fangs, this surprisingly violent Pok\u00e9mon can gnaw away even thick concrete with ease."},{"version":"white-2","text":"With its long fangs, this surprisingly violent Pok\u00e9mon can gnaw away even thick concrete with ease."},{"version":"x","text":"It whittles its constantly growing fangs by gnawing on hard things. It can chew apart cinder walls."},{"version":"y","text":"The webs on its hind legs enable it to cross rivers. It searches wide areas for food."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Raticate\u2019s sturdy fangs grow steadily. To keep them ground down, it gnaws on rocks and logs. It may even chew on the walls of houses."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Raticate\u2019s sturdy fangs grow steadily. To keep them ground down, it gnaws on rocks and logs. It may even chew on the walls of houses."},{"version":"sun","text":"Its hind feet are webbed, so it\u2019s a strong swimmer. It can cross rivers and sometimes even oceans."},{"version":"moon","text":"Its disposition is far more violent than its looks would suggest. Don\u2019t let your hand get too close to its face, as it could bite your hand clean off."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"People say that it fled from its enemies by using its small webbed hind feet to swim from island to island in Alola."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Its whiskers are essential for maintaining its balance. No matter how friendly you are, it will get angry and bite you if you touch its whiskers."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Its hind feet are webbed. They act as flippers, so it can swim in rivers and hunt for prey."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Its hind feet are webbed. They act as flippers, so it can swim in rivers and hunt for prey."}],"evo":{"name":"rattata","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"raticate","level":1,"min_level":20,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,